                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Flaviae Seve<lb break="no" n="2"/>rill<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> v<lb break="no" n="3"/>ixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>XXXVI</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Flav</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Severin<lb break="no" n="5"/>us coniux c<lb break="no" n="6"/>oniugi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 befindet sich auf der Bekrönung. Zwischen D und M ascia. Das Inschriftfeld ist in der rechten oberen Ecke verwittert und nur schwer lesbar. (B): Z. 2: Oelschig: Flaviae [-]A[-]; Z. 4: Oelschig: XXX[-]I; Z. 5: CIL 13, 05132: Se[--]r(i)n/us; Frei-Stolba - Bielmann: Severinus / coniux.</p>
            </div>
